2021全國高中數理科學競賽培訓營篩選題目答案P1在全域宣告變數A=4，而又宣告本地變數A=3，造成區域變數會遮蔽全域變數(Variable shadowing)，而呈現A=3之效果而sum=0+1+2+3+4=10，迴圈共運作5次 P2(a) 公式解作法:$\mathcal{O}(\ n)$$a_{n}= rac{\sqrt5}{5}([ rac{1+\sqrt5}{2}]^n-[ rac{1-\sqrt5}{2}]^n).$缺點: 多次計算${\sqrt5}$(無理數)造成浮點數誤差 遞迴作法: $\mathcal{O}(\ 2^n)$基底:f(0)=1,f(1)=1遞推式:$f_{n}=f_{n-1}+f_{n-2}$缺點:效率低落層層遞迴，每往下一項接分支成兩項，且許多項重複計算 DP作法:$\mathcal{O}( \ n)$dp[0]=0,dp[1]=1dp狀態轉移式:dp[n]=dp[n-1]+dp[n-2]優化細節:若只需末項，使用兩數覆蓋即可dp[n-1]=dp[n];dp[n-2]=dp[n-1]空間複雜度自$\mathcal{O}( \ n)$降至$\mathcal{O}(\ 1)$ 矩陣快速冪作法:$\mathcal{O}(\ log n)$$f_{0}=1,f_{1}=1$$ egin{bmatrix}{f_{n}} 
ewline{f_{n-1}} \end{bmatrix}= egin{bmatrix}{1} &amp; {1} 
ewline{1} &amp; {0} \end{bmatrix}^{n-1} egin{bmatrix}{f_{1}} 
ewline{f_{0}} \end{bmatrix}$舉例:$23=(10111)_{2}=2^4+2^2+2^1+2^0$說明: 每次都將轉移矩陣做平方並更新，取末位若是1則乘入，否則不乘入如:$ egin{bmatrix}{1} &amp; {1} 
ewline{1} &amp; {0} \end{bmatrix}^{23}= egin{bmatrix}{1} &amp; {1} 
ewline{1} &amp; {0} \end{bmatrix}^{2^4} egin{bmatrix}{1} &amp; {1} 
ewline{1} &amp; {0} \end{bmatrix}^{2^2} egin{bmatrix}{1} &amp; {1} 
ewline{1} &amp; {0} \end{bmatrix}^{2^1} egin{bmatrix}{1} &amp; {1} 
ewline{1} &amp; {0} \end{bmatrix}^{2^0}$Pseudo Code 12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728make matrix trans(轉移矩陣)={{1,1},{1,0}} , base{基底} ={{1},{1}}func mul(matrix a , matrix b): make matrix c for i(0 to 2) for j(0 to 2){ c[i][j]=0 for k(0 to 2) c[i][j] += a[i][k] * b[k][j] } return cend funcfunc fast_pow(matrix m, int times): make matrix tem = trans, ans = {{1,0}{0,1}} for t(n to 0 (n!=0) each time &gt;&gt;1){ if (t &amp; 1){ ans = mul(ans , tem) } tem = mul(tem , tem) } return ansend funcmain:make n = 輸入項數t=fast_pow(trans , n).outout t[1][0]+t[1][1] (b)維護每次運算後末兩位，直到找到重複且連續的兩項。往後的費氏數列將產生循環節，最壞情況也僅需運算10000(100*100)次(每次推算必為定值，不隨n成長)，便能找出循環節。往後查詢便能壓在複雜度$\mathcal{O}(\ 1)$
